â”œâ”€ ğŸ“‹ 5. EMPLOYEE_ROSTER (donnÃ©es HRIS)
â”œâ”€ ğŸ’° 6. BUDGET_DATA (donnÃ©es Finance)
â”œâ”€ âš™ï¸ 7. PARAMETERS (standards, ramp curves)
â””â”€ ğŸ“ 8. CHANGE_LOG (audit trail)
```

### **Permissions**

**Sales Managers (Emma, Oliver) :**
- âœ… Edit : SET TARGETS, BUFFERS CONFIG (override), MONTHLY ADJUST
- âœ… View : TRACK PERFORMANCE
- âŒ Edit : EMPLOYEE_ROSTER, BUDGET_DATA, PARAMETERS

